===Pronunciation===

:kwarts
===Noun===

#Quartz is the most abundant [[mineral]] on the earth's surface. It occurs in a variety of forms, both [[crystal]]line and [[amorphous]]. Found in every environment. There is a complete article at [[Wikipedia:Quartz]]. 

=== Chemical composition ===
*Silicon dioxide, <math>SiO_2</math>
 
=== Physical properties ===

*Moh's Hardness: 7.0
*Specific gravity: 2.6
*Color: Colorless, white, smoky, rose, violet, brown, or almost any color depending on inclusions and impurities
*Luster: glassy, transparent to subtranslucent
*Fracture: conchoidal
*Cleavage: Rhombohedral, but seldom observable
*Habit: Hexagonal - Trigonal trapezohedral

